room_title: Escape room "The Great Car Heist" by Headzup in Las Vegas
review: Our group loves escape rooms and this is the first time to HeadzUP and we'll be back!  We did the Car Heist room and had a great time.  And we got out!!  Jason was our host and was terrific.

room_title: Escape room "The Great Car Heist" by Headzup in Las Vegas
review: The Great Car Heist escape room was pretty fun. I did it with one other person, and it was our first time doing an escape room. It was definitely way too hard for us as a first-timer two person team but still a lot of fun.

room_title: Escape room "The Great Car Heist" by Headzup in Las Vegas
review: One of the best escape rooms I have ever done! You definitely need to try it out when in Vegas!The staff is amaaaaaaaaazing!!!!
